
Install Omnigator on Linux/Unix
--------------------------------

Make sure java run-time is installed. Nothing else is required.

unpack oks_samplers in /home/USER (default) using 
-------------------------------------------------

java -jar oks-samplers.jar

edit startup.sh
===============

cd /home/USER/oks-samplers/apache-tomcat/bin

add:
export BASEDIR=/home/USER/oks-samplers/apache-tomcat

execute
========

./startup.sh
ps waux | grep java should show a java/tomcat process

firefox http://localhost:8080


install your topic map ltm
==========================

put cfengine.ltm in

/home/USER/oks-samplers/apache-tomcat/webapps/omnigator/WEB-INF/topicmaps/cfengine_map.ltm


